        {
            "title": "沙田廣源邨居二狂升12倍！ 兩房263萬易手 買入價25萬勁賺243萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eQmo.DS6QvgcEOwJGVrgGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/19e119991d44889ef897dd21e990a720\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%BB%A3%E6%BA%90%E9%82%A8%E5%B1%85%E4%BA%8C%E7%8B%82%E5%8D%8712%E5%80%8D-%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF263%E8%90%AC%E6%98%93%E6%89%8B-%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E5%83%B925%E8%90%AC%E5%8B%81%E8%B3%BA243%E8%90%AC-100757818.html",
